{"tid":1284924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墳總籲不要再以劉馬車去混淆演說義士 拖兄弟後腿","createTime":"2019-07-04T11:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T17:40:53.000Z","uid":8268,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf776c45402cfde5f130f9a05965549097f4d64","tid":1284924,"uid":8268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"#以下發言同列於墳場新聞<br />\n我很少會刪別人的留言。因為我不同意一言堂，但這次我會選擇刪一些以劉馬車去混淆演說義士的留言。<br />\n我深明白，大家用劉馬車來混淆視聽，是為了保護所有義士，立心善良。我完全同意你們在建制系統的留言區玩膠，令他們鬼打鬼。<br />\n<br />\n但今次刻意剝除口罩的烈士，在他的發言之中，他講明，「我除低口罩，係想畀大家知道，其實我哋香港人真係冇得再輸架啦&hellip;&hellip;再輸，係十年，你諗吓係十年，我哋嘅公民社會就會一沉百踩。」他的目的是用自己的血、自己的身體說服所有中間群眾，所有懷疑這種用生命去延續活動的「傻行為」，已經無得掩耳盜鈴。因為義士的原意就係光明正大。我地也光明磊落地打呢場輿論戰。但如果大家在反建制的系統「玩膠」，消化了他的犧牲，咁係咪你地心中所想的事呢？<br />\n<br />\n既然兄弟已經豁出去，為的就是全港的大義，那麼就不要拖後腿。<br />\n<br />\n#跪謝 #認真 #必要之惡<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100009521310169/posts/2359133321080689?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100009521310169%2Fposts%2F2359133321080689%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=daf4bd62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100009521310169/posts/2359133321080689?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ef458b91288d263a7b31d6a78e7a0e935d634411","tid":1284924,"uid":8268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"368a2981d98d8b775f8963d0179db6e3765020cb","tid":1284924,"uid":8268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:11:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd74ba2ec444015d53fc63f21144da49fb6f1793","tid":1284924,"uid":8268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"125c3d0135c71a419ba4f138d933840f9f325fea","tid":1284924,"uid":8268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"我地要記住義士的本心係想點"},{"pid":"d68079d9aec9eb9c9f21981346a3c156744f87a9","tid":1284924,"uid":8268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:13:34.000Z","msg":"深信佢做得呢個決定都係想比人知道佢的決心"},{"pid":"b79cdd60108c0a0ec69dfeed7d5ff1a4734aa8e5","tid":1284924,"uid":8268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:14:09.000Z","msg":"呢種決心唔可以比on9劉馬車沾污玩膠"},{"pid":"eb9e4e7a42796cf6a102aefe5041ba2d0631c419","tid":1284924,"uid":1524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c45f7471fa041df90034edfd59cf4222c81697d","tid":1284924,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}